title: drive carefully.m4v
description:
This is a 7min video short regarding something that is very dear to my heart.
Please watch this video and heed its warning. I don't want to see anymore people hurt, maimed, or killed as a result of inexcusable stupidity. I don't care if this video is re-tagged, up'd to youtube (it already is- as long as it is talked about.)
Take care and God Bless
